extends layout

block content
  h1= title
  p Welcome to #[em Members only], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

  h1 Dynamic content

  if error
    p Error getting dynamic content.
  else
    p The club has the following record counts:

    ul
      li #[strong Users:] !{data.user_count}
      li #[strong Messages:] !{data.message_count}
  
  if(messages)
   each message in messages
    h1= message.title
